						               													<description>From the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Have a Checkers board? When is the last time you played it? Renew the fun and enjoy-ability of Checkers with The Check Deck! The Check Deck is a card game that accompanies and enhances that dusty Checkers board in your closet and reawakens the excitement! It's fun for the whole family and easy to understand and play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rules are simple.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Each player is dealt seven card.&amp;#10;2. A player can either play a card or make a normal checkers move.  Examples of cards are: Move two pieces one space each:  Switch one of your pieces with one of you opponents piece: Turn any of your pieces into a king.&amp;#10;3. As per checkers rules, a move is defined as moving a space, a jump, a double jump, etc.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each deck contains two each of 17 individual cards for a total of 34 playing cards and one rules card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
